latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Yashwantgad Fort is located in Redi, Maharashtra, near the Maharashtra-Goa border. It is located on a small hill North of Jaitapur creek. It is a tree-entangled ruin that looks out over the beaches of the south Maharashtra coast. 
Yashwantgad fort is also know as redi fort 😊

latestIgtvVideos.title: Nazar hati durghatna ghati⚠️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Have been to cab de ram a lot of times but never been here to a hidden mini heavy flow waterfall .. 
This waterfall directly connects to the Arabian sea (cab de ram beach) 
This is dangerous on its side as flow of water is heavy and slight mistake in placing your foot can take your dead body directly into the sea ⚠️
If you visit pls take your garbage back and keep the location cleAn💚
